 \int_{\partial M}\sum_{i=1}^n \color{red}{x_i} \,dx_1\wedge dx_2\wedge \cdots \wedge \widehat{dx_i}\wedge \cdots \wedge dx_n = \mathrm{Vol} (M). 
 d(x_i \,dx_1\wedge dx_2\wedge \cdots \wedge \widehat{dx_i}\wedge \cdots \wedge dx_n) \\ = d x_i \wedge dx_1\wedge dx_2\wedge \cdots \wedge \widehat{dx_i}\wedge \cdots \wedge dx_n \\ = (-1)^{i-1} dx_1\wedge dx_2\wedge \cdots \wedge dx_i\wedge \cdots \wedge dx_n. 
 \int_{\partial M}\,x\,dy\wedge dz+y\,dx\wedge dz+z\,dx\wedge dy \\ = \int_{\partial M}\,x\,dy\wedge dz - y\,dz\wedge dx+z\,dx\wedge dy \\ = \int_{  M}\,d(x\,dy\wedge dz) - d(y\,dz\wedge dx)+ d(z\,dx\wedge dy) \\ =  \int_{  M}dx\wedge dy\wedge dz = \mathrm{Vol}(M). 
